OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FAndy Burnham is set to pledge growth
OL,8,Fand commit to Labour's budget rules as
OL,9,Fhe seeks to burnish his economic
OL,10,Fcredentials after Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,11,Fresignation left him all but certain
OL,12,Fto enter No 10.
OL,14,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor is
OL,15,Fexpected to give a speech on fiscal
OL,16,Fpolicy next week, as first reported by
OL,17,FThe Times, after returning to
OL,18,FWestminster as an MP following his
OL,19,FMakerfield by-election victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
