CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782188270
OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FTalks are also said to be taking place
OL,8,Fabout a prospective new-look Cabinet,
OL,9,Fwith Energy Secretary Ed Miliband and
OL,10,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood both
OL,11,Ftipped as potential candidates to
OL,12,Freplace Rachel Reeves as chancellor.
OL,14,FBut Mr Burnham's allies said no jobs
OL,15,Fhad been given and no deals made as of
OL,16,FMonday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
