OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FThe prospect of a coronation for the
OL,8,Fformer mayor looked increasingly
OL,9,Flikely on Monday as his main rival,
OL,10,Fformer health secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,11,Fbacked him to succeed Sir Keir.
OL,13,FHowever, Darren Jones is said to be
OL,14,Fweighing up whether to launch a
OL,15,Fleadership bid, which could complicate
OL,16,FMr Burnham's plans, after reports that
OL,17,FStarmer loyalists were urging him to
OL,18,Fstand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
