PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782188270
OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FSources close to the Chief Secretary
OL,8,Fto the Prime Minister said he was not
OL,9,Fcurrently minded to run in a contest
OL,10,Fbut that he would want assurances on
OL,11,Feconomic policy, amid concerns among
OL,12,Fsome of potential unease in the
OL,13,Fmarkets.
OL,15,FIf Mr Burnham is the only candidate to
OL,16,Freceived the support needed to stand
OL,17,Fin the contest for the vacant Labour
OL,18,Fleadership, he could become prime
OL,19,Fminister in mid-July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
