PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782188270
OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FIn an emotional statement outside No
OL,8,F10 on Monday, the Prime Minister
OL,9,Facknowledged he had lost the support
OL,10,Fof his MPs and promised an "orderly
OL,11,Fhandover of power" to his successor.
OL,13,FDefending his record, he pledged to
OL,14,Fgive the next leader "my full and
OL,15,Funequivocal support, knowing that they
OL,16,Fwill inherit a Britain that is far
OL,17,Fstronger and fairer than the one I
OL,18,Finherited two years ago".
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@RO]vD@VOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
