CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782188270
OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FOn Monday evening, Sir Keir and his
OL,8,Fwife Victoria hosted No 10 staff for
OL,9,Fdrinks in the No 10 garden, where they
OL,10,Fthanked those present for the support
OL,11,Fthey had given.
OL,13,FLady Starmer told them: "I just wanted
OL,14,Fto say thank you from me.
OL,16,F"I obviously love Keir and support him
OL,17,Fas much as I can, but there's only so
OL,18,Fmuch I could do, and it's you guys who
OL,19,Fgave that support day in, day out, and
OL,20,FI am personally really grateful for
OL,21,Fthat. So, thank you all."
OL,26,@uD@YOUxD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
