PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782188270
OL,3,CBurnham to give speech on economy
OL,4,Cafter Starmer resignation clears way
OL,5,Cto No 10
OL,7,FMr Burnham praised Sir Keir's "huge
OL,8,Fservice to our country" but said his
OL,9,Fresignation "marks the beginning of a
OL,10,Ftransition".
OL,12,FHe said: "The Labour movement has
OL,13,Falways been at its strongest when it
OL,14,Flooks forward with confidence and
OL,15,Fpurpose.
OL,17,F"This is what we will do from here and
OL,18,Fwe will make sure this transition is a
OL,19,Fpositive process of renewal for our
OL,20,Fparty and our country."
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@WO]qD@MOUrD@KO]tD@JOUyD@AOU|D@
